  "page": "House Goodbrother (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>Several houses from the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a> share the name <b>Goodbrother</b>:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\"><img alt=\"House Goodbrother.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/20px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/30px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/40px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\">House Goodbrother</a> of Hammerhorn, one of the most powerful houses on <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Wyk\" title=\"Great Wyk\">Great Wyk</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother_of_Corpse_Lake\" title=\"House Goodbrother of Corpse Lake\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/20px-None.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/30px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/40px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother_of_Corpse_Lake\" title=\"House Goodbrother of Corpse Lake\">House Goodbrother of Corpse Lake</a>, a cadet branch</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother_of_Crow_Spike_Keep\" title=\"House Goodbrother of Crow Spike Keep\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/20px-None.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/30px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/40px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother_of_Crow_Spike_Keep\" title=\"House Goodbrother of Crow Spike Keep\">House Goodbrother of Crow Spike Keep</a>, a cadet branch</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother_of_Downdelving\" title=\"House Goodbrother of Downdelving\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/20px-None.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/30px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/40px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother_of_Downdelving\" title=\"House Goodbrother of Downdelving\">House Goodbrother of Downdelving</a>, a cadet branch</li></ul></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother_of_Orkmont\" title=\"House Goodbrother of Orkmont\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/20px-None.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/30px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/40px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother_of_Orkmont\" title=\"House Goodbrother of Orkmont\">House Goodbrother of Orkmont</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother_of_Shatterstone\" title=\"House Goodbrother of Shatterstone\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/20px-None.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/30px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/40px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother_of_Shatterstone\" title=\"House Goodbrother of Shatterstone\">House Goodbrother of Shatterstone</a>, on <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Wyk\" title=\"Old Wyk\">Old Wyk</a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403121637\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.023 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.072 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 49/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 195/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1598/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.030/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.45 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   62.248      1 -total\n 99.11%   